name: Level Up: The Gamer Girls
description:
The gamer girls have picked up some goodies, made themselves comfortable and are ready for a good game!

Easy win:
Keyboard Сtrl+D - Complete Level

FEATURES

  • 🎮 Beautiful artwork
  • 👾 Animation scenes
  • 🧩 Relaxing music
  • 🕹️ CG Gallery Mode
  • 🧸 Puzzle game

    In the game, your goal is to cut the items to win the level in order to restore the pictures.
